title: New York Gets Its Man, Dez Blasts Dallas, and the Endowment Effect | GM Street (Ep. 274)
description:
The Ringer's Michael Lombardi and Tate Frazier jump right into the Jets signing Sam Darnold (02:00) and other news around training camp (05:00), before looking at the issue between Roquan Smith and the Bears (18:45), how Todd Gurley's contract will affect Aaron Donald (24:45), Dez Bryant's beef with the Cowboys (31:00), and the passing of Tony Sparano (37:00).
